h4 Any player
p
    | A player with this ability has no rear arc. In effect, it does not matter 
    | which direction the player faces when attempting to take an action such as 
    a(href="/actions/#{Enums.Actions.CATCH}") #{Constants[Enums.Actions.CATCH]}
    |, or when they are the target of a 
    a(href="/actions/#{Enums.Actions.SLAM}") #{Constants[Enums.Actions.SLAM]} 
    | attempt.
p
    | Note that a player with this ability also has 6 Threat Hexes, instead of 3.